{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2058142, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "条件有问题吧", "timestamp": 1626162905, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058156, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "年收入咋感觉是多余的数据😂", "timestamp": 1626163059, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058188, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉题目的意思是比如说你每年存100，年化投资收益10%，到第五年就会有100*1.1^4+100*1.1^3+……+100这么多钱，然后看什么时候这些钱能达到首付那么多的金额", "timestamp": 1626163246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058193, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "100×1.1^4乘号好像被当成斜体了😂", "timestamp": 1626163313, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058230, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？？咋这么多收藏😂", "timestamp": 1626163658, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058255, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "年收入没用", "timestamp": 1626163834, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058332, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用首付额÷（年存款额+年化收益）", "timestamp": 1626164573, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058340, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "它说让用户输入年化投资收益 它是个定值  应该每年不会变吧（但这也太简单了）", "timestamp": 1626164641, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058353, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他如果是用每年的年存款额去投资，那每年的基数就都在涨，就要先求出年投资收益率，然后像楼上那种思路就对了", "timestamp": 1626164773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058367, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "题里也没说清楚用什么钱去投资啊，也有可能是（年收入－年存款）的钱来投资×收益率＝投资收益，我觉得这么理解应该是对的，条件都用上了，然后同上", "timestamp": 1626164957, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058368, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058353, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 年投资收益率怎么求", "timestamp": 1626164963, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058373, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058368, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 为什么要去“求”，不是说作为输入吗", "timestamp": 1626165010, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058398, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058368, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我上面说了公式了\n（年收入－年存款）×年投资收益率%＝年投资收益\n三个条件都是已知的，收益率就求出来了", "timestamp": 1626165228, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058403, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是年收入减去年存款作为投资也太扯了吧😂\n虽然要把输入全用上好像只能这么理解", "timestamp": 1626165337, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058406, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058368, "tag": null, "text": "然后进一步计算，但也不知道赚到的钱是用来继续投资还是存款，我觉得应该是难的那种", "timestamp": 1626165366, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058416, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058403, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得可以这么理解吧，收到了工资，一部分存起来，一部分用来做投资，但是他也得有生活费啊，就离谱，这题不是很清楚", "timestamp": 1626165493, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058425, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058403, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 反正两种情况都写了", "timestamp": 1626165587, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058450, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058425, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 既然是“年化”收益率应该就是指连续投资", "timestamp": 1626165801, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058457, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058425, "tag": null, "text": "从金融角度就是一个常见的现金流求终值的问题", "timestamp": 1626165881, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058499, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "公式如下：\nF=P×(1+i)N(次方) \nF：终值\nP：本金\ni：利率\nN：利率获取时间的整数倍", "timestamp": 1626166252, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058534, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058450, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 连续投资是肯定的了，不能考的那么简单，就是不知道它是用什么钱投资了，他要是把“投资率”改成“存款利率”就彻底不用考虑“年收入”了", "timestamp": 1626166547, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058546, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": 2058534, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是的\n所以两种情况都写一下吧😂", "timestamp": 1626166686, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2059925, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不加入一下目标房首付每年的上涨比例吗？有可能永远都买不起目标房的呀", "timestamp": 1626179328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2065734, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 401355, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "无小学期作业吧哈哈哈  cz也没明白", "timestamp": 1626252835, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 106, "w": 941}, "likenum": 14, "pid": 401355, "reply": 24, "tag": null, "text": "有谁学经济的给讲讲，这tm该怎么算", "timestamp": 1626162889, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1626252836, "url": "hb/hbxodpdpjnaj4zpmajrrh2qkzqbcbsd7.jpeg", "vote": {}}}